# Testing Specification

## 1. Test Framework
- **Runner:** <!-- Vitest, Jest, pytest, flutter_test -->
- **Mocking:** <!-- vi.mock, mocktail, unittest.mock -->
- **Coverage:** <!-- v8, istanbul, coverage.py -->

## 2. Test Structure
```
tests/
├── unit/
├── integration/
└── e2e/
```

## 3. Conventions

### Naming
- Files: `*.test.ts` / `*_test.dart` / `test_*.py`
- Names: Describe expected behavior

### What to Test
- Happy path, error cases, edge cases, integration points

### What NOT to Test
- Implementation details, third-party internals, generated code

## 4. Coverage Targets
| Layer   | Target | Minimum |
|---------|--------|---------|
|         | >=90%  | 80%     |
| Overall | >=75%  | 65%     |

## 5. Test Data
<!-- Factories, fixtures, seeds, frozen times -->
